AceD Coin
Cryptocurrency
AceD is the native currency used to fuel the creative and fun AceD Ecosystem which includes Gaming Hub, Streaming and Dashboard.
AceD Streaming
Share your Victories
AceD streaming allows anyone and everyone to share their life, their emotions and their greatest success on all popular games, all while being rewarded by spectators in AceD
AceD GamingHub
Play / Win / Spend
AceD is the unique crypto currency for each game with the Gaming Hub. The principle is simple: Play, Trade or Earn AceD, Spend
AceD Dashboard
The info you need
ACED Dashboard is a platform that will offer useful tools to end-users and potential business partners. ACED merchants will be able to extract key information such as network statistics, number of unique addresses, adoption rate and other market trends.
AceD Snap
Capture / Upload / Earn
ACED Snap is an application that allows users to peer through the eyes of a photographer.  ACED Snap will allow sharing of photos along with the ability to earn tips from other users.
